description:
Steps:
            1. Open the page 'https://demoqa.com/modal-dialogs'
            2. Click the button "Large Modal"
            3. Verify title text
            4. Verify content modal text
            5. Click the exit "x" button
            6. Repeat step 2
            7. Click the "Close" button
            8. Repeat step 2
            9. Click outside the modal (modal-overlay)
